{"tid":6253,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[旅行]元旦去日本","createTime":"2016-11-27T09:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T09:50:46.000Z","uid":21261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eea28a0e40348cd7855d48a9263ce2bb4edc2861","tid":6253,"uid":21261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"想趁新年去放鬆下，想31/12至3/1去日本九州<br />\n但聽講日本新年係大節，鋪頭景點都唔會開，今年2/1都係假期，係咪兩日啲鋪頭景點都關門，4日入面冇左兩日好似唔抵去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6d893395d3d6ba89926ee586ea02835c3da3b3","tid":6253,"uid":21261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:20:28.000Z","msg":"毒撚去旅行求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425a2deffef435e0e1ca147f41050535a0b86a52","tid":6253,"uid":18304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:27:52.000Z","msg":"一樣跨年<br />\n但平安夜到日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec5e8146212b77ce65e24d88bee6ed39c8b78ae","tid":6253,"uid":21261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一樣跨年<br />\n但平安夜到日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打去日本邊到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80feebf3163273acb7d11186904332a1ab862448","tid":6253,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:47:09.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 元旦去日本係一件好戇居既事。<br />\n日本人跨年會返哂鄉下過年，好多鋪頭都休息，多數1月7日之後先正常營業，同埋佢地倒數反應唔會好熱烈，唔當一回事"},{"pid":"41ec2122a9df1f1a4326ef9bf024f3bfe5fd9100","tid":6253,"uid":21261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得罪講句 元旦去日本係一件好戇居既事。<br />\n日本人跨年會返哂鄉下過年，好多鋪頭都休息，多數1月7日之後先正常營業，同埋佢地倒數反應唔會好熱烈，唔當一回事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打咁講唯有睇下有冇第二啲地方去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}